description: Follow live text commentary, score updates and match stats from Bristol Rovers v Stockport County in League One.
title: Bristol Rovers 1-1 Stockport County
title_page: Bristol Rovers 1-1 Stockport County - BBC Sport
maintext:
Bristol Rovers have won three of their last four Football League games against Stockport County, though did lose the reverse fixture this season 2-0 in August.
Stockport County will be looking to record a first Football League double over Bristol Rovers since the 1995-96 season, after winning the reverse fixture at Edgeley Park 2-0 in August.
Bristol Rovers have won each of their last two home league games, last winning three on the bounce in April 2022 (run of 5).
